body:

The 2024 edition of PyCon DE & PyData Berlin took place 22–24 April 2024 at the bcc Berlin Congress Center. Browse the [archived talks](talks/) and [speakers](speakers/) below, or revisit the [original conference site](https://2024.pycon.de/).
